      "content": "That's a bit too generic. These are our highest-paying clients—they care about the nuance. They need to know that even though the speed is increasing, the quality of the personalized itineraries and the deep historical knowledge of their specific preferences might feel different with the new model. Can you flesh this out to emphasize the level of detail and \"human-like\" empathy we currently provide, so they understand what might be lost in the switch?",
